title: Returning player
body: {{champion:32}}  I haven't played 3 years . I had to change name and password because or inactivity.  But all my champs and skins are not on account and its lvl 1 with no points or anything...... am I doing it wrong? Hopefully my stuff isn't deleted.

replies.body: We don't delete content on an account, even if it's been inactive for a long time. Can you ensure you're logging in to the right account? Sometimes if you have multiple accounts tied to a specific email or with similar usernames, it's easy to get confused.
